title: 12/23/20 HOUR 2 - Booger McFarland
itunes:title: 12/23/20 HOUR 2 - Booger McFarland
description:
Dan Patrick has former NFL player Booger McFarland join the show to talk the difference for him in playing against Tom Brady & Peyton Manning. DP thinks the Nets looked very good in their season opener, but how good were the Warriors? The only sure fire QB in this upcoming draft is Trevor Lawrence.
